{"id":232686304,"title":"#超簡單  台式泡菜  食材隨手可得","content":"https://i.imgur.com/brOyBDa.jpg\n\n［食材］\n高麗菜   半顆\n紅蘿蔔   適量\n辣椒      適量\n\n［醃料］\n鹽   一小匙\n糖   量米杯半杯\n醋   量米杯半杯\n\n\n［步驟］\n1. 高麗菜洗淨後剝碎，梗用刀背剁一剁\n2. 用一個口大點的盆子裝，接著揉碎高麗菜（像用洗衣板揉衣服那樣），直到有點菜汁出來\n3. 放紅蘿蔔、辣椒\n4. 鹽、糖均勻灑滿\n5. 最後淋醋（每個地方都要淋到）\n6. 冰冷藏一天後拿出來拌勻\n7. 再冰一天就完成囉✅\n\n冰兩天是最理想最入味的！\nhttps://i.imgur.com/PL3cBXC.jpg","excerpt":"［食材］，高麗菜   半顆，紅蘿蔔   適量，辣椒      適量，［醃料］，鹽   一小匙，糖   量米杯半杯，醋   量米杯半杯，［步驟］，1. 高麗菜洗淨後剝碎，梗用刀背剁一剁，2. 用一個口大","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"d7db42a8-bedb-4ea2-96a7-c9034f4dd89a","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-12-14T14:40:07.443Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-14T14:40:07.443Z","commentCount":4,"likeCount":60,"tags":[],"topics":["泡菜","烹飪","在家輕鬆做","懶人料理","臭豆腐"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"烹飪","forumAlias":"cooking","school":"沙漠美人魚🧜‍♀️","department":"poi779988","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":60}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/brOyBDa.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/PL3cBXC.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"a204cb7d-0a67-49e0-accf-1798c68e79d6","url":"https://i.imgur.com/brOyBDal.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/brOyBDal.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/brOyBDal.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-14T14:40:07.443Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-14T14:40:07.443Z"},{"id":"a204cb7d-0a67-49e0-accf-1798c68e79d6","url":"https://i.imgur.com/brOyBDa.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/brOyBDa","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/brOyBDal.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-14T14:40:07.443Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-14T14:40:07.443Z"},{"id":"66f8371e-97a2-4031-b21a-0e56d00c3c00"